data.description: Nestled amongst the redwoods and blue sky in sought after Scotts Valley awaits the home you have been looking for. In 5 min you are in the drive thru at Starbucks, enjoying Sky Park or shopping at the new Target in the highly desirable Scotts Valley School District. This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath includes a chef's kitchen with stainless steal appliances, open floor plan, large family room and separate laundry room on one level so everyone is close but has their own abundant space. Downstairs awaits your large garage with an additional bonus room, spaces and nooks for bikes, toys, office, gym- the possibilities are endless, what do you need the space for? There is a literal zen garden, a wrap around yard that leads to your multi level deck that includes a hot tub and an outside dining area right off the kitchen- all under open sky with redwoods that frame the property beautifully. There is a feeling of peace around every corner, making this your get away while being close to everything
